  <title>Changing the Ruler Orientation</title>

  <media its:translate="no" type="image" src="figures/orientation.png">
    <p>Changing the ruler's orientation</p>
  </media>

  <p>You can rotate the ruler in vertical position.</p>

  <steps>
    <item><p>Click the menu button (<media its:translate="no" type="image" src="figures/open-menu-symbolic.svg"/>) in the left-side corner of the ruler.</p></item>

    <item>
      <p>
        Click the vertical button to rotate the ruler vertically.
        Click the horizontal button to rotate the ruler back in the horizontal position.
      </p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>You can also change the orientation of the ruler by dragging its corners or by clicking the mouse middle button.</p>
